title: Sgt. Papers - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico with Sgt. Papers performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded March 16, 2023.

Songs:
Ya Levántate
SGTP
Se Siente Bien / No Es Para Todos
Diosito
Sandwich De Monda
En Las Nubes

Felipe García - Vocals, Guitar
Iván García - Drums

KEXP Live from Mexico: Vive Latino is a partnership with Vive Latino and Indie Rocks! Magazine

Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico

Host: DJ Chilly
